{"tid":2504783,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【看電影學英文】：concur ！","createTime":"2021-04-26T06:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T20:12:18.000Z","uid":118346,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"163f2d7ad5bde31825620533b6d1f6ac7358a2cb","tid":2504783,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"【看電影學英文】<br />\n<br />\n李奧納多主演的「神鬼交鋒」(Catch Me If You Can)相信大家都不陌生。一個十幾歲的毛小孩Frank Abagnale竟可以偽造支票詐騙銀行、假冒機師、醫師甚至是律師，把周遭的人唬得一愣一愣，實在是不得不佩服他對人性的了解。<br />\n<br />\n劇中有一幕精彩的橋段，假扮醫師的他在被迫要對病患進行初步診斷，為了不讓自己的身分曝光，巧妙地用一句話掩飾了自己的無知。他說了甚麼呢&hellip;.<br />\n<br />\n他說: 「Do you concur? (你贊同嗎?)」。這其實是他從電視上與醫院有關的影集現學現賣來的。但這兩個實習醫生被他這麼官威很大的反問，便以為主治醫師是在測驗他們的能力，頓時瞠口結舌，急忙說出自己的看法。聽到實習醫生的建議，Frank他老兄就順勢地同意其中一位實習醫師的治療方式，急忙閃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n今天要分享的不是如何假冒醫師(或是李奧納多的演技有多神)，而是要學學Concur 這個字的用法。<br />\n<br />\n基本上Concur 的意思和用法和Agree相同，但是Concur 通常用在比較正式的場合，有點「贊同」或「你我得出相同結論」的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n以下有幾個例句給大家參考：<br />\n<br />\nDo you concur?<br />\n你同意／贊同嗎？<br />\n<br />\nI concur with your suggestion. <br />\n我贊同你的建議。<br />\n<br />\nWe strongly concur with this recommendation.<br />\n我強烈贊同這個推薦。<br />\n<br />\nThe authors concurred with the majority.<br />\n作者們贊同主流的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">這個字比較正式，大家不用刻意一定要用在生活中。但是知道了也是挺不錯，大家千萬不要聽成 Hong Kong 唷！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nDo you all concur? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6141e7b3c3ac2a2db12884c5018cd9e421e6bdfc","tid":2504783,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"What 7 u say ar?"},{"pid":"4c29d65290b676d7a168c93f536b8ed639ee7ce8","tid":2504783,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"concur 聽錯hong kong真心太誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a4eac4b897a719e7fcf188afa6a543c035409e","tid":2504783,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"當年學識呢隻字都係因為catch me if you can <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8991de1149866afa59110606a4dff93c8012d16d","tid":2504783,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a4eac4b897a719e7fcf188afa6a543c035409e","tid":2504783,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"當年學識呢隻字都係因為catch me if you can <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"里安納度係咁問人concur?之後走去嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f77b9b0dc0c3ca4d0d1b3a92caff129f074ab2","tid":2504783,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cctoy"},{"pid":"38e50850e9a54ec312eafc21e56dd07a2c8df652","tid":2504783,"uid":236422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a4eac4b897a719e7fcf188afa6a543c035409e","tid":2504783,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:57:39.000Z","msg":"當年學識呢隻字都係因為catch me if you can <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T20:12:18.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}